    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CategoryName], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[DepartmentId], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId]

) AS [t0] ON [b].[AuthorId] = [t0].[Id]
